OL,6,FThe two women have told about their
OL,7,Fexperiences as the PSNI publishes a
OL,8,Frevised framework to align its
OL,9,Fresponse to violence against women and
OL,10,Fgirls (VAWG) to that of terrorism and
OL,11,Fserious and organised crime.
OL,13,FThree women have been murdered in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland in the last month,
OL,15,Ftaking the total to 30 women and girls
OL,16,Fkilled by men in the region from 2019.
OL,18,FThe former partner of Chelsea
OL,19,FHamilton, 32, was jailed last year for
OL,20,Fassault, threats to kill and
OL,21,Fpossession of an offensive weapon
