OL,6,FMs Hamilton was subjected to three
OL,7,Fyears of coercive control and physical
OL,8,Fabuse in her relationship and when she
OL,9,Ftried to leave, she was shot at with a
OL,10,Fcrossbow that narrowly missed her and
OL,11,Fphysically assaulted for a number of
OL,12,Fhours.
OL,14,FHer ex-partner, who was training to
OL,15,Fbecome a professional MMA fighter at
OL,16,Fthe time, left her with multiple
OL,17,Finjuries.
OL,19,FShe said: "I developed a stutter when
OL,20,Fspeaking to people and began feeling
OL,21,Flike I wasn't even a real person.
