OL,3,CDomestic abuse survivor urges other
OL,4,Cwomen to seek justice
OL,6,F"There are so many women out there who
OL,7,FI know feel the same and are silenced,
OL,8,Fliving in fear. It's not right.
OL,10,F"Through the police's action plan,
OL,11,Fthey want more women to come forward
OL,12,Fand put their trust in them to put
OL,13,Ftheir perpetrator in jail. That's what
OL,14,Fthey did for me."
OL,16,FShe added: "No woman should live their
OL,17,Flife in constant fear, walking on
OL,18,Feggshells and isolated from family and
OL,19,Ffriends. It is no life.
