OL,6,F"They make you feel like what they are
OL,7,Fdoing is your fault in some twisted
OL,8,Fway and that there is a chance you
OL,9,Fwon't be believed. Well, I was
OL,10,Fbelieved and it does get easier."
OL,12,FJane, 23 (not her real name) joined a
OL,13,Fband in the summer of 2022.
OL,15,FWithin the band was a 50-year-old man,
OL,16,Fwho for the next six months
OL,17,Fpersistently contacted her online,
OL,18,Ffollowed her and her family members,
OL,19,Fgave her unwanted gifts and threatened
OL,20,Fto kill himself if she didn't speak to
OL,21,Fhim.
