OL,7,Fand the PSNI secured a Stalking
OL,8,FProtection Order, whereby if he made
OL,9,Fcontact with or came near Jane again
OL,10,Fhe would go to jail for the maximum
OL,11,Fterm of five years.
OL,13,FShe said: "I was mentally tortured by
OL,14,Fthis man, there was no escape from him.
OL,16,F"When I blocked him, he found another
OL,17,Fway to contact me online.
