OL,9,Fphone."
OL,11,FIn September 2022, the PSNI launched
OL,12,Fits first Tackling Violence against
OL,13,FWomen and Girls Action Plan using the
OL,14,Fthen national framework for delivery.
OL,16,FTwo years on, officers have made 3,025
OL,17,Farrests under new legislation
OL,18,F(domestic abuse, stalking and non-
OL,19,Ffatal strangulation).
