OL,6,FThey have also put in place two
OL,7,Fstalking protection orders using new
OL,8,Flegislation.
OL,10,FSince the VAWG Action Plan was
OL,11,Flaunched, 80 arrests have been made on
OL,12,Faverage each month for the domestic
OL,13,Fabuse offence, there have been an
OL,14,Faverage of 17 arrests each month for
OL,15,Fthe offences of stalking and
OL,16,Fthreatening and abusive behaviour,
OL,17,Fwith 77 arrests each month for non-
OL,18,Ffatal strangulation.
OL,20,FIn the 12 months to July 2024 there
