OL,6,F"Too many women and girls in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have lost their lives at the
OL,8,Fhands of men and it has been publicly
OL,9,Facknowledged by the Chief Constable
OL,10,Fand our senior leadership as a whole,
OL,11,Fthat pre-dating our action plan there
OL,12,Fwere shortcomings in our response
OL,13,Fwhich is unacceptable.
OL,15,F"Over the last two years we have
OL,16,Fworked extremely hard at building
OL,17,Frelationships with key partners,
OL,18,Fbolstering our training and
OL,19,Fchallenging our own thoughts and
OL,20,Fbehaviours in this space.
