OL,6,F"As a result of targeted resourcing
OL,7,Fand relentlessly pursuing perpetrators
OL,8,Fwe have seen a reduction in VAWG
OL,9,Foffences and an increase in outcome
OL,10,Frates for victims."
OL,12,FHe added: "There is no doubt that we
OL,13,Fhave made significant progress in our
